ing: 2 pounds stew meat, trimmed and cubed
3 (10.75 ounce) cans condensed cream of chicken soup
des: "Easy, quick and delicious. This stew is cooked in the slow cooker, so all you have to do is heat up some egg noodles and you've got dinner!"
ins:
Spray the inside of a slow cooker with the vegetable cooking spray. Add the meat and the soups to the slow cooker.
Cook on low setting for 8 to 10 hours.
Prepare noodles according to package directions.
When stew is ready, pour over the noodles and serve hot.
